snippet.title: In the Black - Ray Tracing Comes to Starfighter Inc.
snippet.description:
Formally known as Starfighter Inc., In the Black is a multiplayer, space combat simulator brought to us from the developers of Crysis and Star Wars: X-Wing. Expect the beta to come later this year, and even ray tracing support down the line!

GeForce host Julian Huguet: https://twitter.com/jhug00

In The Black Teaser Trailer: https://youtu.be/IqBqHbvsSt0
Impeller Studios: https://impellerstudios.com
In the Black: https://intheblack.gg

Impeller Studios' Twitter: https://twitter.com/impellerstudios  
Impeller Studios' Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ImpellerStudios/
